# 🔐 Password Generator – SoftGrowTech Task

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is developed as part of the SoftGrowTech Task.
It is a simple and responsive **Password Generator** designed to create strong and secure passwords instantly.

The application provides a clean user interface and allows users to customize passwords by selecting options like numbers, symbols, and uppercase letters.

---

## 🚀 Features

* Generate random passwords
* Include Numbers option
* Include Symbols option
* Include Uppercase letters
* Simple and clean UI
* Responsive design
* One-click password generation

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript

---

